provenance: Pierre Auguste Renoir [1841-1919], France. Possibly Durand-Ruel, Paris, France, by 1900 [1]. Jacques Laroche [4]; Durand-Ruel Family Collection, Paris, France [5]; Durand-Ruel, Paris, France and New York, NY, by 1941 [6]; Sam Salz, Inc., New York, NY, by 1965; purchased by Museum of Art, Carnegie Institute, Pittsburgh, PA, October 1965 [7].
